KGOLOKO Thobejane is back! One of the most colourful characters in SA football, Thobejane, is back at Baroka FC. Thobejane is known for his humorous interviews that always leave football fans in stitches. He has re-joined the club, and he will be in charge of the DStv Diski Challenge team. This is after he smoked a peace pipe with club boss Khurishi Mphahlele. Thobejane is known for legendary quotes such as: “Football will kill you, it will kill you a real death! You will die because of football.” The club terminated Thobejane's contract in March 2018 following a protracted suspension.